transcript.title: Resignation of Ted Baillieu
transcript.content:
Sydney

The resignation of Victorian Premier Ted Baillieu tonight is significant news for all Victorians.

This decision must have been a very difficult one for Mr Baillieu and for his family.

I wish Mr Baillieu all the best for the future.

I will seek to work in the interests of all Victorians with Mr Baillieu's successor, Denis Napthine.
